      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="56b9ba7a-112c-47cb-91c5-ece18467af93" type="Noun">
          <Vi>Bộ khởi động (xe); món khai vị</Vi>
          <En>A device that initiates the operation of an engine, or a small dish served before the main course.</En>
          <Example>He turned the key and the starter engaged with a smooth hum.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="ac9ba2c5-d18c-436a-b259-64b0ce7a699e">
              <Vi>Người thợ sửa xe kiểm tra bộ khởi động khi xe không nổ máy được.</Vi>
              <En>An automotive technician checks the starter when a car fails to start.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="b90805d3-124d-44dd-b7c0-caf91d4c72f9">
              <Vi>Trong nhà hàng, món khai vị thường là súp hoặc salad.</Vi>
              <En>In a restaurant, a starter is often soup or salad served before the main dish.</En>
            </Situation>
          </Situations>
